02/03

Yield KeyWord
yield (bla) - control comes back to who called the function and bla is returned
example
def make_page
    page << make_header ()
    page << yield
    make << make_footer ()
end

def one_page
    make_page do 'Hello'
    or
    make_page {'Hello'}
end

